{"tid":186402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"亨利轟奧斯爾交唔足貨！","createTime":"2017-04-04T07:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T10:42:30.000Z","uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f990103fff879288560ae4c4d2ac2d2e13161e","tid":186402,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:29:47.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b59d8fbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴退役隊長亨利批評兵工廠現役中場奧斯爾沒有穩定地交足貨，而有時的表現更不在應有水準。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴周日在主場只能以2:2逼和曼城，兵工廠進攻中場奧斯爾（Mesut Ozil）雖然開出角球造就德國同胞梅斯達菲，跳頂跛網成2:2，並錄得為阿仙奴於各項賽事的第50次助攻，該名2014年世界盃冠軍隊得主仍成為眾矢之的。<br />\n<br />\n兵工廠傳奇射手亨利（Thierry Henry）最近便加入批評行列：「奧斯爾可踢得更乾淨俐落，去年所有人都在稱讚他。他今年陷於於困局，因他不能恆常交足貨。」亨利補充：「當他穿上阿仙奴球衣，有時候未能踢出兵工廠所需的水準。」<br />\n<br />\n曾協助法國勇奪1998年世界盃冠軍的亨利又謂：「我極之欣賞他的風格，現時演出低迷的他若處身當年我效力那支兵工廠，他已被韋托特、伊度、列文，甚至簡奴衝著他說話。當他狀態佳，便難以抵擋。他是世界盃冠軍人馬，在皇家馬德里贏過錦標，亦為阿仙奴捧過2次冠軍獎盃。但他必須經常有出色的表現，不能夠時好時壞。」"},{"pid":"2a9b20753f008ae83076c5facef24972afc39e68","tid":186402,"uid":80792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T07:49:47.000Z","msg":"有爭勝心就唔留阿仙奴啦。。。"},{"pid":"1db351b1579c6d9e8647e539336fb4b6d32946ae","tid":186402,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:37:15.000Z","msg":"表演時好時壞咪符合阿仙奴水準囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1756dd0fa18e0038f16806a6fe42f67ea33689cf","tid":186402,"uid":57382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:45:07.000Z","msg":"98世界杯關享利咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b54a3526777d22025b0cf9a258c4f3febae7fee","tid":186402,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T09:47:00.000Z","msg":"韋托柒有資格話人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde726f5c70f2bd763defa56219e80b00c73ecf9","tid":186402,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"喺到咁搏做乜<br />\n山狗咁搏咪又係咁<br />\n鳩 hea 下得閒射下波唔好"},{"pid":"487b8ce87984c4514dba35dc4f048bacfa16d963","tid":186402,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:28:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>98世界杯關享利咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入咗3球 都叫有貢獻"},{"pid":"d3146481b7e8794c60eaffefafba06703a794e11","tid":186402,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T10:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有爭勝心就唔留阿仙奴啦。。。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}